Name: Project Dark Sky
About the game: I'm sorry but this game will no longer be supported Maya wakes up in the least expected place, at the least expected time...and remembers nothing. She meets people who advise her, but their intentions seem to be different and contradictory. Whom to believe? Whose side should she be on? Is there only one and correct answer? All this seems to have something to do with the space station and the experiment called Project Dark Sky. Game Features in Early Access: first chapter of the story Side-scrolling action 2D controls combo-based fighting system exploration of world with the replayability of a rogue-lite more YOU fight more skills YOU have Secret rooms Overcome fearsome enemies in a hostile environment - one type of enemys 11 levels 3 combos 'Project dark sky' is metroidvania with some side-scrolling beat 'em up game elements about searching for an answer to the question of what is true and what is not. Our protagonist wakes up in some room with no memory of who she is and how she got there. The characters she meet are trying to answer these questions.
